# Slice overview

This project is split into <N> slices. Each slice is a layer of the system with well-defined file ownership, contracts, and a task list. A single agent works on a single slice at a time.

If you're the primary session, you dispatch work by briefing a worker agent with:
1. The slice file (e.g. `docs/SLICES/01-<name>.md`)
2. `docs/AGENT_HANDBOOK.md` (the rules)
3. `docs/TASK_TRACKER.md` (the progress map)

