## Shared-but-rarely-edited modules (contract core)

These files carry cross-slice contracts. Don't modify without coordinator approval:

- `src/<shared-a>.py` — <what it carries>
- `src/<shared-b>.py` — <what it carries>

If your slice needs to change one of these, leave a "schema changes requested" or "contract changes requested" note in `TASK_TRACKER.md` and wait.

